tion of the best\nvalue for O/H in the interstellar medium (ISM), the O/H ratios observed in\nGalactic stars, and the depletion of gas-phase oxygen onto dust grains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2004 17:18:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
