 well as on the size of the cusp, is also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2004 19:44:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2005 12:02:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2005 17:33:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
